CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 12, 1954, pg. 10, reads: "Founders Day - Alpha Gamma Chi Sorority held its founders day by worshipping at the morning service at Second Presbyterian Church, and then attending a luncheon at Child's Restaurant, Fifth Avenue. Pictured are Sorors Alma Illery, Nancy Lee, Della Vance, Willa Mae Rice, Goldie Hamilton, Agatha Simms, Mary Clark, Myra Johns, Daisy Goodman, Earsley Kincaid. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of members of Alpha Gamma Chi Sorority, including Alma Illery, Nancy Lee, Della Vance, Willa Mae Rice, Goldie Hamilton, Agatha Simms, Mary Clark, Myra Johns, Daisy Goodman, and Earsley Kincaid, posed in Child's Restaurant
